Emma Dickson developed blood clots after taking the contraceptive pill . 
  The clots moved to her lungs and caused a pulmonary embolism which caused her left lung to collapse . 
  The 31-year-old was rushed to hospital and told she had been taking the pill . 
  She was meant to be planning her wedding but ended up thinking about her funeral . 
  Doctors told her she had developed the clots as a result of the synthetic hormones in the pill  . 
  She was due to marry fiance Dougie a month later in Edinburgh . 
 